        <div class="welcome-header">
          <div class="main_wrapper_new">
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0686/9486/8103/files/image_1_1_76d32aab-2b4e-4c68-a411-5a2a219321bf.png?v=1770384836" 
              alt="TSTN"
            >
            <p>WELCOME TO TSTN CLUB</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="welcome-description">
            Join the club. Earn points for every lighting<br>or recovery upgrade and level up your<br>journey with TSTN.
